# Plinth-on-plinth: shared/, templates/, and bin/ are the PRODUCT here —
# fully agent-editable. Only the INSTALLED previous-release copies (the
# instrument judging this repo) are immutable. Patterns use (^|plinth/)
# anchoring so absolute paths match the installed copies but never the
# shared/ sources. (Bash-write matching is weaker for bare relative
# mentions here; the reviewer's tamper rule and the harness CI job are the
# deeper layers.)
(^|plinth/)\.claude/hooks/
(^|plinth/)\.claude/settings\.json$
(^|plinth/)\.plinth/review\.sh$
(^|plinth/)\.plinth/review-schema\.json$
(^|plinth/)\.plinth/plinth-rules\.md$
(^|plinth/)\.plinth/MODELS\.md$
(^|plinth/)\.plinth/protected-paths$
(^|plinth/)\.plinth/config$
(^|plinth/)AGENTS\.md$
